💳 HDFC Bank App Redesign

📌 Project Overview

This project is a **UI/UX redesign of the HDFC Bank mobile application** created using Figma.
The goal of this redesign was to improve **user experience, visual clarity, and accessibility** while keeping the design modern and user-friendly.

---

🎯 Objectives

* Improve overall **user interface (UI)**
* Enhance **user experience (UX)**
* Simplify complex banking tasks
* Make the design more **intuitive and clean**
* Improve navigation and accessibility

